    answer: "Yes. Dolphin designs centrifuge packages to meet the specified hazardous area classification. The design basis, whether NEC Class I Division, ATEX Zone, or IECEx, is confirmed from the project datasheet, area classification drawing, and specification."
  },
  {
    question: "Is FAT available at Dolphin's Warren, Michigan facility?",
